Titolo: ClayFighter 2: Judgment Clay

Anno: 1995

Descrizione: ClayFighter 2: Judgment Clay is a one-on-one fighting video game released exclusively for the Super NES in 1995. It is Interplay's sequel to their 1993 game ClayFighter. The game's name is a parody of the 1991 film Terminator 2: Judgment Day.